{"type": "article", "id": 54385, "title": "Google 注资京东，以及，Yeezy 最新广告被指抄袭 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2018-06-18T23:41:58Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 3134, "name": "Versace"}, {"id": 977, "name": "Tom Ford"}, {"id": 34195, "name": "New Look"}, {"id": 46585, "name": "Yeezy"}, {"id": 779, "name": "Prada"}, {"id": 6419, "name": "Armani"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 574557, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 19, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180619042000hf0v8cyMZk1RL6Tu.jpg", "contents": "<h3 finallycleanhtml=\"true\">一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><strong><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/financial/google-invests-550-million-into-jd-com-1202717067/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Google 向京东投资 5.5 亿美元</a>&nbsp;</strong>| Google 于 6 月 18 日宣布向京东注资 5.5 亿美元。它将获得新发行的超过 2700 万股京东 A 类股普通股，发行价为每股 20.29 美元。&nbsp;双方将“共同开发零售基础设施，以提供更好的个性化购物体验，并减少包括东南亚在内数个市场的阻碍”。京东还表示，它计划通过 Google Shopping 在美国和欧洲等地销售部分商品。</p><p><strong><a href=\"http://us.fashionnetwork.com/news/New-Look-steps-back-from-Chinese-expansion,988917.html#.Wyf3UBIzbOQ\" rel=\"nofollow\">New Look 或中止在华扩张计划</a>&nbsp;</strong>| New Look 原本计划在华开出 500 家门店， 但执行主席&nbsp;Alistair McGeorge 上周日接受美联社采访时称，公司正在梳理全球门店网络，计划缩减规模。目前，New Look 在中国共有 148 家门店，全部为直营。中国也不是唯一需要调整的市场。根据上周公布的财报，截止 3 月 24 日的 2017 财年，New Look 的运营损失已达 7430 万英镑。虽然它此前曾尝试与 Boohoo 和 ASOS 等抢夺年轻消费者，但似乎并不奏效。这家英国零售商目前计划调低价格、扩大目标客群，并缩减男装专门店。</p><p><strong><a href=\"https://www.businessoffashion.com/articles/news-analysis/tapestry-sues-executive-who-accused-former-stuart-weitzman-creative-director-of-sexual-harassment\" rel=\"nofollow\">Coach 母集团 Tapestry 起诉前高管，后者一个月前曾指控 Stuart Weitzman 前创意总监性骚扰</a>&nbsp;</strong>|&nbsp;Tapestry 于本周一向纽约州最高法院起诉该集团前产品研发副总裁&nbsp;Thomas Gibb，认为其违反劳动合同，参与到另一鞋履品牌&nbsp;Tidal 的运营中。Thomas Gibb 同时于周一被解雇。一个月前，Gibb 曾指控 Tapestry 旗下品牌 Stuart Weitzman 前创意总监 Giovanni Morelli 对其实施性骚扰。该指控引来广泛关注，并最终导致 Morelli 离职。</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p><strong><a href=\"http://www.vogue.co.uk/article/kris-van-assche-unveils-first-berluti-campaign\" rel=\"nofollow\">Kris Van Assche 出任 Berluti 艺术总监以来的第一组广告片出炉</a></strong>。</p><p>新广告由 Jamie Hawkesworth 担任摄影师，Mauricio Nardi 任造型师。三张黑白影像中，三位模特裸露上半身，手里拿着 Berluti 经典的 Alessandro 牛津鞋。Kris Van Assche 还请平面设计师组合 M/M Paris 依据 1895 年品牌创始时鞋楦上所刻的字母重新设计了 Logo。</p><p>Kris Van Assche 于今年 4 月加入 Berluti，此前掌舵 Dior Homme 长达 11 年。不同于同样刚加入 LV 的 Virgil Abloh 和加入 Dior Homme 的 Kim Jones，Kris Van Assche 不会参加 6 月 19 - 24 日举行的巴黎男装周。他的首个 Berluti 系列将于今年 1 月发布。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201806190216047trhf3QiZ4kCub1G.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.295062\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180619021616Un6xvTDyc1PpoHiC.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.295062\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180619021628QTUsw4hyFN5KP6We.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.295062\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong><a href=\"https://wndrmuseum.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">草间弥生的“无限镜屋”系列作品将首次登陆芝加哥 WNDR 博物馆</a></strong>。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180619070150GtTCbLu6S9QJ2gjM.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180619065800UyqlDwXi6dkBOgax.png\" data-ratio=\"0.667774\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180619070141LCP1AWmJjxiFrdUM.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.749023\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180619070250cFpY0QrRWPo16X9n.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.692383\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180619070311QY16JgPTESeip8fX.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.749023\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180619070338iU71gxeFZMQcpt2I.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong><a href=\"http://wwd.com/runway/mens-spring-collections-2019/milan/tom-ford/review/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Tom Ford 男装 2019 春夏系列在米兰发布</a></strong>。</p><p>设计师将本季重点放在了外套上：正反两穿的格纹外套、黑白防风夹克、吸烟风衣。色彩以象牙白、奶油色、浅粉为主，材质多变——灯芯绒、亚麻、棉、羊毛。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180619025337HjGEsZY0Toew4kKt.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180619025402rkeMcgNWFDtxhlGf.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666179\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180619025410oK698qMpeudfRENw.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666179\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180619025418jSV7qROMz9hp2mHr.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666179\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180619025425C2GJrfic7yzK8Bps.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666179\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180619025432BEpwoyRUC0je68iq.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666179\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180619025440zPqBAwguDTiFmRar.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666179\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180619025450gPeBLt93FkOcHCN0.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666179\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180619025458zpiuI6qRSGUl24nP.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666179\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180619025507Dy1peml45YgEz9Jc.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666179\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180619025514X1RwFWxnHiZBhEsg.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666179\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180619025527zUQCVcwXhDENyxlB.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666179\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180619025546jxZhs0GcI3HovyfA.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666179\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180619025558lX42hxyHoAqaprcs.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666179\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180619025616cu7weYA3slQdvJri.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666179\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180619025633u6gfTFsQv12jzOIo.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666179\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180619025646Gv5Afp3ygIcwlLib.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666179\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180619025658ZtKlDcyF06ExV1OH.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666179\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201806190257394cvVWuXSz2rPYOno.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666179\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong><a href=\"https://www.lofficielusa.com/men/versace-spring-2019-menswear#image-16388\" rel=\"nofollow\">Versace 男装 2019 春夏系列在米兰发布</a></strong>。</p><p>新系列张扬炫丽。荧光色和花朵印花叠加在一起，传统剪裁的西装配上宽松的牛仔裤。“这是一群不在乎规则的男性，有想法，自己选择自己的风格”，设计师说。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180619035612wM9g2pChX3UNFHJq.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.503132\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180619035600Q8jAJ4prdcthYUvV.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.503132\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180619035623veD6Gsj4UuEwZLpa.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.503132\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201806190356318kyUXFzH4s0fqQKW.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.503132\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201806190356431V3EY7INcOmbLSiy.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.503132\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201806190356544PJXrU0aEmyYRe9C.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.503132\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180619035702g40zay5vfkQOSsBn.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.503132\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180619035712OIrNyCXlhwZtgmVT.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.503132\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180619035722CrsuVENqla6oBz58.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.503132\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180619035730XJOcqedU0tzSrEL1.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.503132\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180619035751TQ0fgR6AvpYFomzL.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.503132\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180619035811A0irYsIETVORvfnN.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.503132\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180619035823uptTzGJaV0wfq8kE.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.503132\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180619035837jAJFsdO8PuM0xgSH.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.503132\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180619035903vdCYoWizf86PeZEk.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.503132\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180619035935hfMICp5uGP3qTn6m.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.503132\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180619035944KP4cV8pgtbHxdvfr.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.503132\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180619040011QxHKTvYl9EPAoXq8.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.503132\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201806190400247dwP4Ekps653Fim9.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.503132\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180619040040LC5H8xvIDSPAahcO.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.503132\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180619040059srMp1hUDvjlWALK3.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.503132\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180619040114AYN0i3Xpea8LPoVx.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.503132\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180619040139nBgd0jhPGIvLAu3i.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.503132\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180619040127cEaAYf91l8xUndXR.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.503132\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180619040159ozpmVfq7eBn1c96G.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.503132\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201806190402121B4Avc2soTVnZbkM.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.503132\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180619040223g1DmoMWJNRYxIz7L.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.503132\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180619040236lcvVa1UjyInFhKZ7.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.503132\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2018061904025156w28WNQCmglSn3B.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.503132\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180619040326Gycl5Dfvtx8z1jU0.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.503132\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180619040337Svi4xCrf1BR3Q6Gh.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.503132\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180619040354682QhZwD5bVzLem1.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.503132\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201806190404077yMo1N6uSihUqs3p.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.503132\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong><a href=\"https://www.vogue.com/fashion-shows/spring-2019-menswear/prada\" rel=\"nofollow\">Prada 男装 2018 春夏系列在米兰发布</a></strong>。</p><p>Miuccia&nbsp;Prada 在这一季希望塑造的男性形象是“羞涩而性感”，兼顾辨识度和实穿性：糖果色的 Polo 衫搭配传统剪裁的西装，或 60 年代迷幻色彩 Polo 衫外套一件针织衫。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180619065049iR7sfpoxHCadUWhe.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180619065111KYbyqLMZsmHRj1EC.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180619065123oTVea8E3ypWxkHwU.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201806190651380CY64FAx8vlqDEQu.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180619065153qUpRIS83WXsONwlx.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180619065204HI0UmdNJTkpcZy4t.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201806190652142fwyvbAug3etrP7q.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180619065225fQ8OnHw6GcICj2gd.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180619065246UQ75sxS4Mncd8IwV.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180619065300S5IRfZFC90GtnjQr.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong><a href=\"https://www.vogue.com/fashion-shows/spring-2019-menswear/giorgio-armani/slideshow/collection#27\" rel=\"nofollow\">Giorgio Armani 男装 2019 春夏系列在米兰发布</a></strong>。<br></p><p>Giorgio Armani 没有像其它品牌那样追逐街头元素、狂野的动物印花、荧光色以及对八九十年代的怀旧情绪。设计师仍然强调通过对比例的把握塑造优雅绅士的形象，双排扣外套、宽松的风衣和长裤等创造出慵懒的氛围。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201806190716506QuOPFkMe57vDBwg.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180619071701TVLMDs5ehvc40PFy.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201806190717090WSGYnB9ENxu6zwm.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180619071721KtFg9UDky2I3VPqu.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180619071731e5pKwIjzqdyb8Dlh.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201806190717407DqIr1f5aiyFgVNY.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180619071754osVDTISf9AJzBjNF.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180619071803XGn2NugqFHWY74UD.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180619071811IepiXOdz0Y8WTl2k.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180619071819JRwkOFaEg4e8fsnS.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180619071835GXL5wsv8KI2otJYV.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong><a href=\"https://www.elle.com.au/fashion/yeezy-season-6-campaign-diet-prada-17828\" rel=\"nofollow\">Yeezy 最新广告被指抄袭</a></strong>。</p><p>提出抄袭嫌疑的仍然是被称为“时尚警察“（fashion police）的 <a href=\"https://instagram.com/diet_prada/?utm_source=ig_embed\" rel=\"nofollow\">Instagram 账号 Diet Prada</a>。上周，Yeezy 刚刚发布 Yeezy 500 Supermoon Yellow 系列广告，找来网红 Clermont Twins、Veneda Budny、Kristen Noel Crawley 等全裸出镜，引发争议。</p><p>Diet Prada 指出，广告拍摄创意与 2015 艺术家 Rita Minissi 的“Self and other”系列影像作品在构图、背景以及人物姿态上高度相似，并放出了对比图。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180619032941SiDzHxMOLpkbQAFc.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>上为 Rita Minissi 作品，下为 Yeezy 广告</figcaption> </figure></div><p>题图来自 <a href=\"https://www.wallpaper.com/fashion/fashionweeks/menswear-ss-2019/milan/prada-at-milan-fashion-week-mens-ss-2019\" rel=\"nofollow\">Prada Men's Spring 2019</a><br></p>"}